## types.PropPath type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type PropPath<T, U> = U extends keyof T ? {
    [Key in U]: T[Key];
} : U extends `${infer P}.${infer RT}` ? P extends keyof T ? {
    [Key in P]: PropPath<T[Key], RT>;
} : never : never;
```
